{"tid":1466733,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家對唔對得住天琦","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T00:57:18.000Z","uid":151535,"like":54,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b4aea339652c7efe5718f5e7eb2d5f778d2712f1","tid":1466733,"uid":151535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"「不要被仇恨支配自己」<br />\n「不要被仇恨支配自己」<br />\n「不要被仇恨支配自己」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知道大家721 811 之後都好嬲。<br />\n但係我地係非常時期，就唔可以受情緒影響我地嘅判斷。<br />\n我地做所有嘢嘅時候，都需要以今次運動為先。<br />\n<br />\n如果我地唔識控制自己情緒，我地同警犬有咩分別。<br />\n如果我地搞到記者同埋阻住救護，我地同警犬有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n大家成日笑吳卓羲衰衝動，我希望大家都盡可能冷靜思考一下。勇武同冷靜之間並冇衝突，兩者合為一體先係最好嘅勇武。<br />\n<br />\n大家要控制自己，時刻記住天琦嘅忠告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天琦仲係監獄入面，唔好令佢失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb28a5b6049b81341f1b52424e18c2a896be0cc4","tid":1466733,"uid":151535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:06.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"2a69910d5c136f20992f80c2536ab9d58d243d63","tid":1466733,"uid":151535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:16.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"b541bd45b448e63b8397cc932b75cde57f406b8f","tid":1466733,"uid":74869,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:24.000Z","msg":"其實佢請幾十個普通人著黑衫 捉一個預定俾佢捉既鬼<br />\n就可以帶動成個機場既風向 同連登分化 <br />\n我地要做既係和理非現場停止捉鬼 因為對我地無害性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申 不割 做左就做左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37fdf74689bb5a3fa546f56ccd7816aa57762d58","tid":1466733,"uid":233530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f6cd36c652d21783f1318077f91791a67ce7a227","tid":1466733,"uid":100787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:52.000Z","msg":"槍口對外 不分不割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bde74b75f98477815e3becce101aa758b38e03","tid":1466733,"uid":151535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:01.000Z","msg":"一定唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6325370c8f84976c3b27a8187691996c76b4bf43","tid":1466733,"uid":18639,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:08.000Z","msg":"我明白手足們十分憤怒，但請手足冷靜少少，捉鬼係唔會令我地羸，而係會令我地分化令我地輸。你諗下我地有幾多個手足，你捉到鬼既機率高d定係捉到自己人既機率高d？而就算真係捉到隻鬼，咁之後又有咩野做到？捉鬼重要d定羸返香港重要d？<br />\n本來今日班popo過到黎仲打爆左一個人既頭流哂血，聽朝頭條就係班popo入機場既第一滴血。依家因為捉鬼，仲要捉到果個真係記者黎。雖然佢十分可疑，但事實上佢既身份真係記者。咁聽日既頭條就變左做示威者捉錯記者，完美咁比人spin左風向。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 唔會割蓆 大家共同進退 只係想大家停止捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596650e7fc3cb4ef2e75fb1f7d0495bb4f8b1d3c","tid":1466733,"uid":245347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:11.000Z","msg":"我認同你<br />\n無聲勝有聲"},{"pid":"f5f611c25724a24e20a2a42074b156124658ccea","tid":1466733,"uid":110402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:11.000Z","msg":"公安扮暈俾唔俾佢走好？"},{"pid":"c2094a2f70fe50209ec77d0ae6cb9d02f5905dfc","tid":1466733,"uid":17184,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:23.000Z","msg":"唔知天琦得知811當晚既事件又忍唔忍得住怒憤呢"},{"pid":"14c7c9580b39110de6ed4c846c988b16e491b457","tid":1466733,"uid":114553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3de06b0a395ae129b3098efa7ce52d3b1f897967","tid":1466733,"uid":112433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:45.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"4d78444267f8646c678cfdd3019d3d721819195b","tid":1466733,"uid":272976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2094a2f70fe50209ec77d0ae6cb9d02f5905dfc","tid":1466733,"uid":17184,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:23.000Z","msg":"唔知天琦得知811當晚既事件又忍唔忍得住怒憤呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:59.000Z","msg":"你哋答我，你哋對得住死控嘅烈士咩？"},{"pid":"c516138d1e233f332f15971b1358f406090f6636","tid":1466733,"uid":53954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:56:06.000Z","msg":"衝動一定係輸<br />\n大家冷靜"},{"pid":"4e94c1b7139bbbdcf1a4bf3ebc592f4b0d374417","tid":1466733,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8772c5c2521680e9ea6afb485eada7be3b932438","tid":1466733,"uid":111898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:09.000Z","msg":"要推 大家一定要記住呢句說話"},{"pid":"793badc4a0edcbc9172616c2526b4ef02f75a9aa","tid":1466733,"uid":148570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">STAY SANE </span></span>"},{"pid":"e491045da01123e582d040cf52528beb92ed6647","tid":1466733,"uid":204385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:06.000Z","msg":"冷靜 獨立思考"},{"pid":"033d4abdf16b5fd5d865040d9baea70af28ae80b","tid":1466733,"uid":13308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家係抗爭者唔係驅魔人, 唔好執著邊個鬼, 認清目標, 五大訴求, 缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"39449e795b280ca91f57b5af8e2ff2d8fb3ecd95","tid":1466733,"uid":151535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f5f611c25724a24e20a2a42074b156124658ccea","tid":1466733,"uid":110402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:11.000Z","msg":"公安扮暈俾唔俾佢走好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:17.000Z","msg":"我覺得大家知道佢係公安嘅時候，最好嘅方法係比文宣巴打推大佢。反正佢走咗大家都認得佢，佢做唔到啲咩衰嘢。<br />\n<br />\n當然，小弟個膽好細，今日唔係現場，唔敢妄下定論。但係都係果句，核彈都唔割。"},{"pid":"591ff6458698a69465830c7db265cb9537981d0e","tid":1466733,"uid":284180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:47.000Z","msg":"明明今日人肉封離境大堂係好成功<br />\n到到開始捉到公安後 就帶動晒大部份人過去圍觀<br />\n跟住又唔知點解t2又慢慢開始恢復返服務<br />\n其實 好心啦 入黎機場係捉鬼咩？下次做呢d野既時候 諗清楚為乜野入去機場啦！<br />\n捉到隻鬼 又點？ 又私刑 又推救護 而家一鋪清袋 乜幫助都無 真心今晚好洩氣"},{"pid":"ea13c83b69418a46c58d28ead0eab11ac1d6d5f9","tid":1466733,"uid":279555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:09.000Z","msg":"不要被仇恨支配<br />\n<br />\n721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"70d0b29c0ca78ee0a65accbef2e1e09fc2351711","tid":1466733,"uid":285872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"67938123c64556a0d52764672aadda974bad6b80","tid":1466733,"uid":151535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:12.000Z","msg":"不要說 push<br />\n試著說 「不要比仇恨支配自己」"},{"pid":"d44b880a56cdc63b0f0d2e24f89a9da49a875188","tid":1466733,"uid":232921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:02.000Z","msg":"如果比仇支配，我地同狗有乜分別？大家清醒下"},{"pid":"6ae7198b9dfa3eb36e7b88a6e0eb86b43d41dac6","tid":1466733,"uid":151535,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:11.000Z","msg":"如果大家好嬲嘅時候，瘋狂咁loop<br />\n「不要被仇恨支配自己」<br />\n「不要被仇恨支配自己」<br />\n「不要被仇恨支配自己」"},{"pid":"aa6ad64d3aa3cba5550e576079317a55d76ee054","tid":1466733,"uid":151535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:39.000Z","msg":"有鬼固然係要捉，始終要防止811咁<br />\n但係捉完咪由得佢比first aid 救走囉<br />\n記住我哋入機場係有兩個最大用處<br />\n癱瘓機場同埋文宣<br />\n留咗隻鬼喺度唔係好做到以上兩個目的"},{"pid":"bf267b331d02f2ab830dbc9cb5144e39a00abad9","tid":1466733,"uid":151535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"幫推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ae457b4535ced6af00e136b8d7cd8f491b398b","tid":1466733,"uid":151535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:10:23.000Z","msg":"太多post推唔郁<img src=\"/a